(616, 1, '2015-10-27 06:46:46', '2015-10-27 06:46:46', 'Ykings is mainly based on the disciplines calisthenics and gymnastics. Both sports are reknown for the most demanding and challenging skills and moves in bodyweight training.<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nMastering a skill requires to go at it step by step. The adaptive nature of the sport and your progress towards a skill is embedded in essential exercises called progressions. This is why at Ykings we talk about progressive bodyweight training.\r\n\r\nProgressive bodyweight training (PBT) secures gradual development towards advanced bodyweight exercises and elite skills such as the muscleup, human flag, front lever and many more.\r\n\r\nThe purpose of the Ykings workout concept is to guide you efficiently and healthy towards mastering your most desirable bodyweight skills. Consider to workout not only for your fitness, but strength, body control and skills at the same time.\r\n\r\n<em>#StriveForProgress</em>', 'The sport behind Ykings', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ykings-2', '', '', '2016-06-08 14:15:21', '2016-06-08 14:15:21', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.76/Projects/ykings/?page_id=616', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(620, 1, '2015-10-27 06:48:33', '2015-10-27 06:48:33', '<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Get ready to be pushed\r\n</strong></p>\r\nYkings is divided in a basic free version and YkingsPro with a subscription based dynamic personal Coach.\r\n<div id="ufaq-body-3r7-1451-11" class="ufaq-faq-body ufaq-body-1451">\r\n<div id="ufaq-post-1451" class="ewd-ufaq-post-margin ufaq-faq-post">\r\n\r\nIn the free version of Ykings you can try multiple workouts, engage with the community and get a feeling what Ykings is all about.\r\n\r\nWe have developed YkingsPro for those of you, who seek an adaptive path to work on their body transformation, simply want to pursue skills while getting strong and fit. YkingsPro includes the following benefits compared to the free version:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>No limits</strong> - access all workouts, excercises, skills, progressions and HIIT runs</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Personalized workout plans</strong> - take advantage of weekly workout plans which are dynamically adapted to your feedback\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>availability</li>\r\n 	<li>workout intensity</li>\r\n 	<li>focus track</li>\r\n 	<li>raids</li>\r\n 	<li>skill- and fitness level</li>\r\n 	<li>goals</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Full workout days</strong> - progress in a healthy way. Get various warmups, fundamentals (pre-workout, dynamic stretching and mobility), workouts (circuit-, sets &amp; reps training) and stretching routines</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Skill raids</strong> – pick your wanted skill and receive professional skill trainings to push your progress to the next level</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Progression formula</strong> – master elite skills (muscleup, front lever, human flag and more) with essential step by step progressions and ally exercises automatically integrated in your workouts</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Guidance</strong> – all progressions and exercises include video tutorials with pro tips and range of motion</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Freestyle</strong> – track your own workout sessions and log them in your profile</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Community</strong> – share &amp; receive tips and tricks from other athletes, friends and featured athletes &amp; find athletes and trainings spots around to you</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'What to expect from the app?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'coach', '', '', '2016-06-09 10:46:55', '2016-06-09 10:46:55', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.76/Projects/ykings/?page_id=620', 0, 'page', '', 0),
