(640, 1, '2015-10-27 08:58:18', '2015-10-27 08:58:18', 'Ykings Smartphone Apps were developed to bring a versatile sport to a bigger audience. Equipped with a individualized and adaptive coach, users can simply choose their goals and wanted skills and start to go after multiple goals at once. Ykings smartphone apps are available on iOs and Android. In the basic version, user can try out workouts and get a feeling of the sport and its community. For those of you who seriously want to get in shape, build strength and hunt down skill we developed the YkingsPro. Check out the benefits of using your personal coach and what to expect.\r\n\r\n<a href="https://itunes.apple.com/in/app/ykings/id1099738889?mt=8"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1398" src="http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/app-store.png" alt="app-store" width="184" height="63" /></a><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ykings.norse"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1400" src="http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/google-play.png" alt="google-play" width="185" height="63" /></a>', 'Ykings Smartphone Apps', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'smartphone-application', '', '', '2016-06-10 13:56:10', '2016-06-10 13:56:10', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.76/Projects/ykings/?page_id=640', 0, 'page', '', 0);
