(643, 1, '2015-10-27 08:58:39', '2015-10-27 08:58:39', 'A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart. I am alone, and feel the charm of existence in this spot, which was created for the bliss of souls like mine. I am so happy, my dear friend, so absorbed in the exquisite sense of mere tranquil existence, that I neglect my talents. I should be incapable of drawing a single stroke at the present moment; and yet I feel that I never was a greater artist than now. When, while the lovely valley teems with vapour around me, and the meridian sun strikes the upper surface of the impenetrable foliage of my trees, and but a few stray gleams steal into the inner sanctuary, I throw myself down among the tall grass by the trickling stream; and, as I lie close to the earth, a thousand unknown plants are noticed by me: when I hear the buzz of the little world among the stalks, and grow familiar with the countless indescribable forms of the insects and flies, then I feel the presence of the Almighty, who formed us in his own image, and the breath ', 'Knowledge', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'knowledge', '', '', '2015-10-27 08:58:39', '2015-10-27 08:58:39', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.76/Projects/ykings/?page_id=643', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(646, 1, '2015-10-27 09:03:34', '2015-10-27 09:03:34', 'Ykings GmbH was founded in November 2015 by sports enthusiasts and professionals. The young company is focused on providing state of the art fitness &amp; health solutions via smartphone applications.\r\n\r\nThe first version of the app was released in May 2016. The company is well connected with the popular disciplines calisthenics, gymnastics and bodyweight training. To support beginners but also to provide a high level of versatility to advanced athletes, demanding skills were broken down into essential step by step exercises (progressions) and support exercises (allies).\r\n\r\nThe solution provided is a fully adaptive workout and training experience that considers fitness and skill level, weekly availability and intensity. The workout concept is made for beginners and advanced athletes and is independent of time and place. It can be used alone or with a community of like-minded athletes. Download from the app stores - for iOS and Android.', 'About us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'policy', '', '', '2016-06-07 09:32:07', '2016-06-07 09:32:07', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.76/Projects/ykings/?page_id=646', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(649, 1, '2015-10-27 09:03:55', '2015-10-27 09:03:55', '<strong>General Terms and Conditions of Business</strong>\n<strong> of Ykings</strong>\n\n<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Contents:</span>\n\n1. Details of service provider\n2. Preliminary remarks on the YKINGS Training Concept\n3. Scope of these Terms and Conditions; Customer group; Contractual language\n4. Conclusion of the contract\n5. Products and services\n6. No medical treatment or advice\n7. Prices and payment\n8. Ownership of rights and limitations of use\n9. Prohibited activities; User content\n10. Authorization of access and users’ responsibilities for access data\n11. Blocking user access\n12. Technical requirements; user’s obligation to perform data backup\n13. Right of cancellation\n14. Liability for faults or defects\n15. Liability\n16. Term of contract and termination\n17. Applicable law\n\n&nbsp;\n\n1. Details of service provider\n\nYkings GmbH, Schöllerstr.13, 72160 Horb am Neckar, Germany, telephone +49 (0)89-2031 7866, email: support@ykings.com, entered in the Commercial Register of Stuttgart District Court (Amtsgericht Stuttgart), register number HRB 754631, represented by Managing Director Philipp Heinrich Steinhöfel.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n2. Preliminary remarks on the YKINGS Training Concept\n\nYkings GmbH (hereinafter also “we”, “us” or “Ykings”) is the developer of the Ykings Training Concept. As part of the Ykings Training Concept, we have designed a range of training units known as "Workouts", which are based on body weight training. The majority of the exercises are from the discipline calisthenics and are therefore very challenging. An integral part of the training concept is gradual development of the body to more and more difficult exercises by subdividing them into individual steps (progressions) – the “Progression Formula” progress mapping system is integrated into the training. We regularly revise and advance our exercise programs and also provide users (hereinafter also “customer” or “you”) with the opportunity to receive personalized coaching under a membership scheme. Acquisition of the mobile app, opening a user account and use of the app are all free of charge. However, within the app additional services incurring charges may be ordered as “in-app purchases”. We regard Ykings as an independent holistic training concept that helps users to develop their physical potential. Ykings is represented in social networks, enabling users to interact and communicate with friends, like-minded others and pro athletes. Be inspired and motivated by the Ykings Community and Strive For Progress. Welcome!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n3. Scope of these Terms and Conditions; Customer group; Contractual language\n\n3.1 The business relationship between us and you is governed exclusively by these Gen-eral Terms and Conditions (hereinafter T&amp;Cs) in the version valid at the time of your application to open a user account and/or the submission of your order.\n\n3.2 The products and services provided by Ykings are exclusively directed at consumers. Customers are consumers within the terms of Section 13 German Civil Code (BGB) provided they enter into a legal transaction for purposes that are predominantly out-side their trade, business or profession.\n\n3.3 The contract may only be concluded with adult natural persons, i.e. persons of full age and capacity. By submitting an order, you confirm that you are at least 18 years old.\n\n3.4 The prevailing language for conclusion of the contract and communication is English.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n4. Conclusion of the contract\n\n4.1 Free acquisition of the “Ykings” app;\n\nIn order to use Ykings, you must first acquire the free mobile app “Ykings” from an app store. Conclusion of the contract for acquisition of the app is between you and the app store operator, and is governed by the user conditions applying to the app store. The contract is generally affected when you click the “Install” button in the app store and, if applicable, enter your app store password.\n\n4.2 Free registration and opening of a user account\n\nYou can use the mobile app to register and open a user account with us free of charge. To do this, during the registration process you must state your agreement with the application of these T&amp;Cs and our data privacy terms by clicking the appropriate box to give a statement of agreement. We then send an email to the email address you have entered during registration; by clicking the “Confirm registration” link in the email, you confirm the opening of your user account. In the next step, you are redirected to an Internet site in which we finally confirm your registration. This step completes the registration process and opens your user account. You can also launch the registration process for opening a user account with us from your Facebook account.\n\n4.3 Acquisition of subscriptions with additional services incurring charges by means of in-app purchases\n\nYou can use the mobile app to acquire a subscription to our services for a period of 3, 6 or 12 months; this subscription, which incurs charges, enables you to use various additional services. By clicking the “Buy” button of an in-app purchase within the app, you submit a binding offer to us to take out a subscription for the selected min-imum period. At this stage you are not requested to input any further billing or pay-ment data as payment is effected via your account with your app store operator.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n5. Products and services\n\nThe scope of the products and services provided in Ykings and usable by you de-pends on whether you are using a free or paid version of Ykings.\n\n5.1 Free use of the products and services\n\nWhen making free use of the app, your use of the products and services is restricted to the basic functions and information described in the app.\n\n5.2 Paid use of the products and services\n\nIf you acquire a paid subscription with certain additional services by making an in-app purchase within the