(1016, 1, '2016-01-11 10:13:00', '2016-01-11 10:13:00', '<strong>After reading this article you will know</strong>\n<ul>\n	<li><strong>what impact your peers have on you</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>why you have to associate yourself with the right people</strong></li>\n	<li><strong>why a dedicated workout group gives you opportunities\n</strong></li>\n</ul>\nBeing in the game of change and new interests, your peer group profoundly impacts your progress. Your peers are a mirror of yourself and influence whom you socialize with, who become members of your network and they are the filter by which you consider all your decisions.\n\nIf you want to achieve a specific goal in your life, get around those people who already achieved your goal. It sounds simple, however most people don’t put enough effort and persistence into choosing a peer group. Truth is, many get out in the working world, and the people around you become part of your peer group just because you happen to see them a lot. They just fall into whatever peer group happens to be the most convenient. Go out there and actively look for people with the same interest. While this is somewhat natural, you miss an opportunity when you don’t proactively choose at least some portion of your peer group. In the fitness world this is your workout group or your social connection to a bunch of like-minded people.\n\n<a href="http://ykings.com/New/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/023.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-922"><img class="aligncenter  wp-image-922" src="http://ykings.com/New/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/023-683x1024.jpg" alt="023" width="406" height="609" /></a>\n\nThe motivation, the advice and the experience you can share with your workout group is priceless. If you haven’t devoted energy to building your relationships, consider doing now. If you are not sure how to find people around you interested the same thing, you have to find your community. Wanna get started? What''s holding you back?\n\nConnect and learn from the pros. Our community grows together. #WeGrowTogether. Ykings brings a community of dedicated people together. Look out for daily advice from Team Ykings and our featured athletes. Strive for progress my friend.\n\nPS: In of our next posts we will cover the benefits of doing HIIT.', 'The power of a dedicated workout group', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-power-of-a-dedicated-workout-group', '', '', '2016-01-11 10:13:00', '2016-01-11 10:13:00', '', 0, 'http://stage.ykings.com/?p=1016', 0, 'post', '', 0),
