(1424, 1, '2016-06-10 09:03:39', '2016-06-10 09:03:39', '<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Learn calisthenics with Ykings</strong></p>\r\nYKMS stands for Ykings Mannfall Sessions. YKMS are free sessions which are offered to create  interest of the gereal public in the sport. We are supporting local groups to offer YKMS as a introduction to the sport with a set standard.\r\n\r\nThe mission is to help all athletes of different fitness and skill levels to progress to the next level or simply get a feeling what the sport is all about.\r\n\r\nYKMS follow a simple schedule that is altered a bit by the local groups which looks like this.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>warmup</li>\r\n 	<li>mobility session</li>\r\n 	<li>skill training and progression class with pull/dip/core&amp;leg stations</li>\r\n 	<li>workout challenge</li>\r\n 	<li>cooldown &amp; stretching</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEverybody is welcome, we always have a beginner class that gets an introduction to the sport, so feel free to join us. Check our <strong><a href="http://ykings.com/New/index.php/our-events/">events webpage</a></strong> or sign in over facebook.\r\n\r\n[facebook id="facebook_53" links="https://www.facebook.com/official.ykings/" width="" layout="standard" colorscheme="light" sendbutton="false" showfaces="false" ]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in getting YKMS to your city,<strong> <a href="http://ykings.com/New/index.php/contact/">contact us</a></strong>. Become a partner and do your part to bring the sport forward.', 'YKMS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'ykms', '', '', '2016-06-10 10:00:07', '2016-06-10 10:00:07', '', 0, 'http://ykings.com/New/?page_id=1424', 0, 'page', '', 0),
