(1427, 1, '2016-06-06 18:09:01', '2016-06-06 18:09:01', 'Ykings GmbH was founded in November 2015 by sports enthusiasts and professionals. The young company is focused on providing state of the art fitness &amp; health solutions via smartphone applications.\r\n\r\nThe first version of the app was released in May 2016. The company is well connected with the popular disciplines calisthenics, gymnastics and bodyweight training. To support beginners but also to provide a high level of versatility to advanced athletes, demanding skills were broken down into essential step by step exercises (progressions) and support exercises (allies).\r\n\r\nThe solution provided is a fully adaptive workout and training experience that considers fitness and skill level, weekly availability and intensity. The workout concept is made for beginners and advanced athletes and is independent of time and place. It can be used alone or with a community of like-minded athletes. Download from the app stores - for iOS and Android.', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '646-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-06 18:09:01', '2016-06-06 18:09:01', '', 646, 'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/06/646-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
