(1517, 1, '2016-06-08 14:14:01', '2016-06-08 14:14:01', 'Ykings is mainly based on the disciplines calisthenics and gymnastics. Both sports are reknown for the most demanding and challenging skills and moves in bodyweight training.<strong>\n</strong>\n\nMastering a skill requires to go at it step by step. The adaptive nature of the sport and your progress towards a skill is embedded in essential exercises called progressions. This is why at Ykings we talk about progressive bodyweight training.\n\nProgressive bodyweight training (PBT) secures gradual development towards advanced bodyweight exercises and elite skills such as the muscleup, human flag, front lever and many more.\n\nThe purpose of the Ykings workout concept is to guide you efficiently and healthy towards mastering your most desirable bodyweight skills. Consider to workout not only for your fitness, but strength, control and skills at the same time.\n\n<em>#StriveForProgress</em>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Learn / Evolve / Master</strong>\n\nRegardless of whether you are a beginner or well-trained person, Ykings is designed to give everyone a starting point and the missing pieces to elevate yourself to the next level.\n\nBesides all kinds of Push, Pull, Full Body, Dips and Core elements, the workout concept also includes mobility and flexibility exercises, High Intensity Interval Training (HIIT) and pure strength workouts.\n\nYkings offers a smart personal coaching function that automatically tailors weekly workout plans according to your personal availability, goals, skills &amp; preferences. Get full workout days with warmups, fundamental pre-workouts, special skill trainings and stretching sessions in addition to achieve your goals. Activate your progressions and define the skills you want to master. Adjust your coach week by week in highly responsive feedback sessions.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>Be socially connected</strong>\n\nBeyond working out, Ykings connects you to a unique community of like-minded people. Follow your friends and our featured athletes and benefit from the extra push of motivation. Share your experience and stay in touch with supporters.\n\n<em>#WeGrowTogether</em>', 'The sport behind Ykings', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '616-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-08 14:14:01', '2016-06-08 14:14:01', '', 616, 'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/08/616-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1518, 1, '2016-06-08 14:15:21', '2016-06-08 14:15:21', 'Ykings is mainly based on the disciplines calisthenics and gymnastics. Both sports are reknown for the most demanding and challenging skills and moves in bodyweight training.<strong>\r\n</strong>\r\n\r\nMastering a skill requires to go at it step by step. The adaptive nature of the sport and your progress towards a skill is embedded in essential exercises called progressions. This is why at Ykings we talk about progressive bodyweight training.\r\n\r\nProgressive bodyweight training (PBT) secures gradual development towards advanced bodyweight exercises and elite skills such as the muscleup, human flag, front lever and many more.\r\n\r\nThe purpose of the Ykings workout concept is to guide you efficiently and healthy towards mastering your most desirable bodyweight skills. Consider to workout not only for your fitness, but strength, body control and skills at the same time.\r\n\r\n<em>#StriveForProgress</em>', 'The sport behind Ykings', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '616-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-08 14:15:21', '2016-06-08 14:15:21', '', 616, 'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/08/616-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(1519, 1, '2016-06-08 14:51:45', '2016-06-08 14:51:45', '<div id="cc-m-8363560395" class="j-module n j-text ">\r\n\r\nThe word <strong><i>calisthenics</i></strong> comes from the ancient Greek words <i>kálos</i> (κάλλος), which means "beauty", and <i>sthénos</i> (σθένος), meaning "strength". Calisthenics is raw and pure bodyweight training and also known as Street Workout. One of the greatest advantages of bodyweight training is that you can do it anywhere, anytime, and there are easier and more advanced exercises to start or evolve with.\r\n\r\nBeginners as well as advanced athletes will find a goal to pursue with the sport. Besides the standard claims of many sports and fitness programms, calisthenics does not only increase your general fitness and get you in great shape, but provides multiple benefits in addition for you.\r\n\r\nProper calisthenics training will promote the growth of lean muscle mass, and increase your strength, mobility, flexibility, agility, and endurance.\r\n\r\nAs you see from the list of benefits of the sport, there is a fine line to competitive gymnastics. In the Ykings workout concept we embedded the adaptive nature of the sport in a comprehensive progressive bodyweight training concept. If you want to be more than just fit, let us hunt down skills and evolve you to a bodyweight master. Welcome to our world.\r\n\r\n</div>', 'What is Calisthenics?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1415-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-08 14:51:45', '2016-06-08 14:51:45', '', 1415, 'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/08/1415-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
