(1522, 1, '2016-06-09 07:03:22', '2016-06-09 07:03:22', '<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Get ready to be pushed\r\n</strong></p>\r\nYkings includes a dynamic coaching function (Coach) that compiles weekly workout plans to your personal preferences. Your virtual coach will develop your body awareness and get you closer to your set goals, 100% tailor-made and adjusted to your fitness level. With the coach you get workout plans that not only get you fit, but strong &amp; skilled at the same time.\r\n\r\nThe coach considers your skill level at all times and will challenge you weekly to progress efficiently. Become comfortable, being uncomfortable and conquer set goals in small guided doable steps. Doesn''t matter if you just started or if you are an old hand at sports. A library of videos will guide you through your workouts if needed.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://ykings.com/New/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/iStock_000051423662_Large-e1455113998137.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-1112"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-1112" src="http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/iStock_000051423662_Large-684x1024.jpg" alt="" width="423" height="634" /></a>\r\n\r\nBesides your personal goals, the Coach will consider your preferences such as\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>availability,</li>\r\n 	<li>intensity,</li>\r\n 	<li>muscle group</li>\r\n 	<li>fitness &amp; skill level.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Learn / Evolve /Master</strong></p>\r\nAs you evolve through the multi-level learning program <a href="http://ykings.com/?page_id=631"><strong>– the progression formula -</strong></a>  you will be able to track and master your strength and skill level. The Progression Formula breaks demanding exercises down into progressions which the coach integrates in your workouts. We demystify demanding exercises such as the one arm pushup, muscleups and many others so that they will become achievable for you.\r\n\r\nSpecify the skills you want to work for and the coach will make sure you learn them. Join Ykings - the healthy step by step approach to achieve your goals - fully customizeable with state of the art smartphone applications.\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">#WeGrowTogether #StriveForProgress</p>', 'Ykings Coach', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '620-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-09 07:03:22', '2016-06-09 07:03:22', '', 620, 'http://ykings.com/New/index.php/2016/06/09/620-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
