(1624, 1, '2016-06-13 08:39:46', '2016-06-13 08:39:46', 'Hey everyone,\r\nI''m Flex_st and not long ago I had a desire to workout but didn''t want to go to people-packed gyms and instead signed up for a trial in a local crossfitbox. The monthly contribution was not exactly what I expected and I researched for alternatives. I fell in love with bodyweight exercises and ultimately encountered Street Workout.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_996" align="aligncenter" width="648"]<a href="http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/IMG_5749-21.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-996"><img class="wp-image-996" src="http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/IMG_5749-21.jpg" alt="IMG_5749 21" width="648" height="432" /></a> Human flag at the top of the mountain[/caption]\r\n\r\nI was ambitious and took on the challenge, I even started my own team with friends (KoalaBars). My friends and the community we got in touch with are the biggest motivation factor for me. What is yours? Embrace the struggle on the way to learn &amp; perform new skills such as the muscleup, front &amp; back lever and so on. The cool thing with Ykings is that you will get workout plans that have your current skill factor integrated in the workouts. This means no research and nothing to woory about... just smash your workouts. Another motivation factor is the progression formula which will permanently motivate you to unlock the next skill.\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_995" align="aligncenter" width="647"]<a href="http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/IMG_5739-21.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-995"><img class="wp-image-995" src="http://ykings.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/IMG_5739-21.jpg" alt="IMG_5739 21" width="647" height="431" /></a> Explosive pushups. Bam![/caption]\r\n\r\nI am an addict to the sport and still progressing. I also want to push the body centered movement further as a whole. Personally I am working to get the planche. Follow me to see closely what I am up to towards achieving that goal.\r\n\r\nFind me in the app under - <strong>Flex_st</strong>', 'Flex_st: On the way to new goals', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1593-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-06-13 08:39:46', '2016-06-13 08:39:46', '', 1593, 'http://ykings.com/index.php/2016/06/13/1593-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
